00:49:09,020 --> 00:49:11,100
You must have been
extremely shocked back then, right?

545
00:49:11,680 --> 00:49:12,920
I'm sorry

546
00:49:15,410 --> 00:49:17,160
I left you all alone.

547
00:49:17,690 --> 00:49:19,400
I tried to find my way back to you,

548
00:49:19,820 --> 00:49:20,680
but...

549
00:49:20,840 --> 00:49:21,840
It's okay.

550
00:49:23,070 --> 00:49:24,560
You weren't to blame at all.

551
00:49:26,070 --> 00:49:28,480
Time travel isn't something
that can be done easily.

552
00:49:32,520 --> 00:49:33,660
No need to blame yourself now, okay?

553
00:49:37,660 --> 00:49:40,720
I searched everywhere for you,

554
00:49:41,760 --> 00:49:42,640
but...

555
00:49:43,070 --> 00:49:44,860
I couldn't find any traces of you.

556
00:49:50,570 --> 00:49:52,340
But now, we're together at last, aren't we?

557
00:49:53,630 --> 00:49:55,600
And we'll never be apart again.

558
00:50:15,580 --> 00:50:17,360
But Phop...

559
00:50:18,640 --> 00:50:20,560
do you remember everything
since the beginning?

560
00:50:21,840 --> 00:50:22,640
No.

561
00:50:24,670 --> 00:50:26,640
Everything came back to me

562
00:50:30,870 --> 00:50:32,800
when I turned 20

563
00:50:33,460 --> 00:50:34,680
last year.

564
00:50:46,160 --> 00:50:47,600
[MOM: Happy birthday, son.
Take care of yourself and eat your meal on time]

565
00:50:47,640 --> 00:50:49,020
[Juju: HBD,
I hope this year is a bit more kinder to you]

566
00:50:49,050 --> 00:50:49,750
[KLA-HARN: Happy Birthday!
Hope you get some proper rest this year, LOL]

567
00:50:49,780 --> 00:50:50,550
[May: Happy birthday, Phop.
May good things come your way]

568
00:50:50,580 --> 00:50:51,380
[NAM: HBD. May fortune be on yourside soon]

569
00:50:51,420 --> 00:50:52,230
[DOOBIED: Happy birthday bro!
Wishing you less stress and more good surprises]

570
00:50:54,250 --> 00:50:55,070
That was a kiss?

571
00:50:55,250 --> 00:50:56,250
Let me show you how it's done.

572
00:50:56,360 --> 00:50:57,730
You keep saying
I once did this and that.

573
00:50:57,760 --> 00:50:59,500
Things aren't the same anymore, are they?

574
00:50:59,560 --> 00:51:00,630
I am more than pleased.

575
00:51:00,680 --> 00:51:02,160
My concern for you is not unrequited.

576
00:51:02,200 --> 00:51:03,070
I spoke in the Phichit tongue,

577
00:51:03,100 --> 00:51:03,730
my Lady.

578
00:51:03,760 --> 00:51:05,240
I told you I'm not Klao!

579
00:51:05,280 --> 00:51:06,380
Stop calling me by that name already!

580
00:51:06,440 --> 00:51:07,960
I shall seek you out...

581
00:51:08,500 --> 00:51:09,880
until I find you

582
00:51:10,080 --> 00:51:11,520
and love you once more.

583
00:51:15,610 --> 00:51:18,570
The memories suddenly rushed into my head,

584
00:51:18,610 --> 00:51:20,080
as if

585
00:51:20,190 --> 00:51:23,450
my past life were connected to this one.

586
00:51:23,580 --> 00:51:25,210
I then started to miss Klao,

587
00:51:25,240 --> 00:51:27,870
who came back after disappearing.

588
00:51:27,910 --> 00:51:31,710
I'm Ms. Nahathai's son,

589
00:51:32,610 --> 00:51:35,040
the deputy from the nearby mango orchard.

590
00:51:35,270 --> 00:51:37,470
Then I remembered what Harn had said.

591
00:51:37,580 --> 00:51:38,370
At last,

592
00:51:38,390 --> 00:51:40,860
Klao had once again been slain,

593
00:51:41,180 --> 00:51:43,920
despite my having already killed him
with my own hands.

594
00:51:48,420 --> 00:51:50,360
That was when I came up with a theory.

595
00:51:50,720 --> 00:51:51,380
A pretty wild one, too.
[Nahathai, Deputy, Mango Orchard]

596
00:51:51,410 --> 00:51:51,800
[Handsome and Beautiful Deputies]

597
00:51:53,280 --> 00:51:53,790
[Phattanatada]

598
00:51:53,820 --> 00:51:54,640
[Results of the Academic Excellence Awards
for Academic Year 2023]

599
00:51:58,440 --> 00:52:00,680
[Nakun Phattanatada]

600
00:52:01,930 --> 00:52:03,540
Klao didn't lose his memories.

601
00:52:06,920 --> 00:52:07,920
Instead...

602
00:52:08,270 --> 00:52:09,360
he came from this present time.

603
00:52:10,690 --> 00:52:11,410
Whoa.

604
00:52:11,750 --> 00:52:12,470
Phop.

605
00:52:14,470 --> 00:52:16,240
What's next?

606
00:52:17,380 --> 00:52:19,440
Did you keep looking for me after that?

607
00:52:20,270 --> 00:52:21,100
Mm.

608
00:52:22,290 --> 00:52:25,280
Then I found out that
you study at the same university as Thee.

609
00:52:25,550 --> 00:52:27,080
Everything I need is on the Internet.

610
00:52:27,660 --> 00:52:29,680
So I went to see Thee at the university.

611
00:52:33,370 --> 00:52:34,500
Nakun's contact.

612
00:52:34,800 --> 00:52:35,800
Here's Nakun's contact, guys!

613
00:52:36,320 --> 00:52:37,270
- His contact!
- Stop!

614
00:52:37,330 --> 00:52:38,410
Stop. You can't do this!

615
00:52:38,440 --> 00:52:39,440
Can you guys see this?!

616
00:52:39,920 --> 00:52:40,840
- Give it to me!
- It's Nakun's!

617
00:52:40,930 --> 00:52:42,150
Hey! This is Nakun's contact!

618
00:52:42,180 --> 00:52:43,720
You can't do this!

619
00:52:43,750 --> 00:52:45,080
You'll get a partner, that’s why!

620
00:52:45,140 --> 00:52:46,560
I don't want one!

621
00:52:47,280 --> 00:52:48,580
Nakun's contact!!

622
00:52:49,130 --> 00:52:50,290
Just seeing you there

623
00:52:50,860 --> 00:52:52,870
already made me want to go and hug you.

624
00:52:53,490 --> 00:52:55,070
But then I thought...

625
00:52:55,480 --> 00:52:57,190
you probably didn't know anything yet.

626
00:52:57,220 --> 00:52:58,080
This is his contact!

627
00:52:58,120 --> 00:53:00,400
You probably hadn't
traveled back in time yet.

628
00:53:01,230 --> 00:53:02,230
Here's Nakun's contact.

629
00:53:02,540 --> 00:53:04,160
It's his contact, Nakun's contact.

630
00:53:05,590 --> 00:53:07,180
Nakun's contact!!

631
00:53:09,190 --> 00:53:10,990
If you had found me first,

632
00:53:11,760 --> 00:53:13,560
everything could have changed.

633
00:53:15,080 --> 00:53:16,770
So all I could do was wait,

634
00:53:17,430 --> 00:53:19,640
just like I did in my past life.

635
00:53:20,120 --> 00:53:21,320
Gosh, how unfortunate.

636
00:53:27,020 --> 00:53:28,450
I called you to help me with my work.

637
00:53:28,970 --> 00:53:30,080
What are you laughing at?

638
00:53:30,560 --> 00:53:31,960
Look at Nakun, my buddy.

639
00:53:32,690 --> 00:53:34,540
He celebrated his birthday last night.

640
00:53:34,900 --> 00:53:37,060
They say bad things happen
when you turn 25, right?

641
00:53:37,680 --> 00:53:38,810
But he's only 20.

642
00:53:39,350 --> 00:53:41,170
Yet he's been bombarded with misfortunes.

643
00:53:43,070 --> 00:53:45,040
That was when I came up with an assumption:

644
00:53:45,230 --> 00:53:48,360
if Harn killed Klao
and made him disappear at the age of 20,

645
00:53:49,220 --> 00:53:50,580
would that bring Nakun back to
the Ayutthaya period

646
00:53:50,600 --> 00:53:52,360
when he turns the same age?

647
00:53:53,040 --> 00:53:54,680
Do you want to help ease his misfortunes?

648
00:53:58,610 --> 00:53:59,920
That's why...

649
00:54:01,240 --> 00:54:02,180
I came up with a plan.

650
00:54:02,520 --> 00:54:04,410
Your mom knows a certain fortune teller.

651
00:54:07,100 --> 00:54:07,970
Listen.

652
00:54:08,390 --> 00:54:09,820
I refuse to take part in anything

653
00:54:09,840 --> 00:54:11,660
that compromises the ethics
of the prophetic craft.

654
00:54:17,020 --> 00:54:18,960
I simply want you to listen to me,
Fortune teller.

655
00:54:20,270 --> 00:54:22,780
It's up to you
whether you believe me or not.

656
00:54:24,520 --> 00:54:26,000
400 years ago,

657
00:54:26,510 --> 00:54:29,320
you were on the very cusp of
becoming the oracle of the court.

658
00:54:29,960 --> 00:54:31,240
But you were cast out,

659
00:54:32,400 --> 00:54:33,960
as you were condemned

660
00:54:34,380 --> 00:54:35,740
for being effeminate.

661
00:54:38,570 --> 00:54:40,320
Are you here to steal my job?

662
00:54:40,920 --> 00:54:43,280
Thus, you ended up as a wandering oracle,

663
00:54:43,600 --> 00:54:45,760
lending aid to others
in whatever ways you could.

664
00:54:48,150 --> 00:54:49,640
This shard of a shooting star

665
00:54:50,320 --> 00:54:52,740
is something you gave to someone.

666
00:54:54,570 --> 00:54:55,580
Does it look familiar to you?

667
00:55:00,990 --> 00:55:01,680
Ah!

668
00:55:03,680 --> 00:55:05,120
This isn't fake.

669
00:55:05,610 --> 00:55:07,220
It's called a 'wishing stone.'

670
00:55:21,980 --> 00:55:23,420
You probably know

671
00:55:24,320 --> 00:55:25,840
what it can do, don't you?

672
00:55:26,630 --> 00:55:28,420
With strong will and determination,

673
00:55:29,510 --> 00:55:32,140
any wish will come true.

674
00:55:33,480 --> 00:55:34,160
Precisely.

675
00:55:35,080 --> 00:55:36,520
It will be yours

676
00:55:38,930 --> 00:55:40,360
if you help me.

677
00:55:46,420 --> 00:55:49,560
I asked the fortune teller
to advise you to return to Ayutthaya,

678
00:55:50,130 --> 00:55:52,120
as it might send you back to the past
and reunite us.

679
00:55:53,760 --> 00:55:54,580
Hey! Nakun!

680
00:55:54,640 --> 00:55:55,440
Nakun!

681
00:55:55,610 --> 00:55:56,260
Klao!

682
00:55:56,360 --> 00:55:57,240
Are you okay, Nakun?

683
00:55:59,250 --> 00:56:01,780
Since then,
I've been keeping an eye on you,

684
00:56:02,360 --> 00:56:04,280
making sure you're safe.

685
00:56:04,520 --> 00:56:05,520
Shit...

686
00:56:10,250 --> 00:56:13,080
And I was actually brought back
to that time period.

687
00:56:14,320 --> 00:56:16,360
Time doesn't move in a straight line;

688
00:56:17,610 --> 00:56:19,600
it moves in cycles,

689
00:56:20,310 --> 00:56:21,520
doesn't it?

690
00:56:26,740 --> 00:56:28,390
Why didn't you say anything

691
00:56:28,720 --> 00:56:30,080
when we were at the hotel?

692
00:56:31,270 --> 00:56:33,120
Even though everything fell into place,

693
00:56:33,940 --> 00:56:35,720
it was only a theory.

694
00:56:36,810 --> 00:56:38,960
There was a chance
that you wouldn't recognize me.

695
00:56:45,310 --> 00:56:46,140
Mm.

696
00:56:46,630 --> 00:56:47,560
Likewise.

697
00:56:48,550 --> 00:56:51,360
I actually wanted to hug you
when we met in front of the hotel.

698
00:56:51,950 --> 00:56:53,800
If you couldn't recognize me

699
00:56:54,520 --> 00:56:55,680
in this lifetime,

700
00:56:55,890 --> 00:56:58,400
people might not only think
I've lost my wits,

701
00:56:59,980 --> 00:57:00,980
but they might even

702
00:57:01,490 --> 00:57:03,000
lock me behind bars.

703
00:57:10,010 --> 00:57:10,960
At first,

704
00:57:11,550 --> 00:57:13,480
I thought it was all just a dream.

705
00:57:14,880 --> 00:57:15,880
If...

706
00:57:16,260 --> 00:57:18,670
it weren't for the clothes I was wearing
when I was transported back here,

707
00:57:19,490 --> 00:57:21,440
I might have thought I'd lost my mind.

708
00:57:24,070 --> 00:57:24,870
Still...

709
00:57:27,800 --> 00:57:28,980
I'm glad

710
00:57:29,470 --> 00:57:30,200
that...

711
00:57:30,930 --> 00:57:33,600
we were finally able to
find one another once more.

712
00:57:36,770 --> 00:57:37,480
Mm.

713
00:57:42,530 --> 00:57:45,000
From now on,
I'll never let you slip away again.

714
00:57:48,670 --> 00:57:51,120
You're going to
get tired of seeing me every day.

715
00:57:57,290 --> 00:57:58,720
If this isn't a sacred place...

716
00:58:02,910 --> 00:58:05,640
Then let's go somewhere else.

717
00:58:06,190 --> 00:58:08,720
Where did you have in mind?

718
00:58:17,540 --> 00:58:19,360
I was thinking of taking you to this event.

719
00:58:20,510 --> 00:58:22,140
It's being held at a nearby university.

720
00:58:24,650 --> 00:58:26,310
[Unsolved Mysteries from Ayutthaya:
A Nobleman's Betrayal,

721
00:58:26,330 --> 00:58:28,480
Corruption in the Opium Trade,
and Records Missing from History]

722
00:58:37,120 --> 00:58:37,700
[Unsolved Mysteries from Ayutthaya:
A Nobleman's Betrayal,

723
00:58:37,720 --> 00:58:38,870
Corruption in the Opium Trade,
and Records Missing from History]

724
00:58:38,900 --> 00:58:40,200
Most strikingly,

725
00:58:40,280 --> 00:58:45,020
the document in question
was written in modern-day English,

726
00:58:45,100 --> 00:58:49,480
a fact that is historically implausible

727
00:58:49,870 --> 00:58:51,800
given the period of time,

728
00:58:51,860 --> 00:58:54,760
in which it is purported to have been produced.

729
00:58:55,320 --> 00:58:56,880
For this reason,

730
00:58:57,520 --> 00:59:00,660
the document has not been accepted

731
00:59:00,680 --> 00:59:04,320
as a reliable historical source.

732
00:59:06,440 --> 00:59:08,070
The text here

733
00:59:09,100 --> 00:59:14,160
makes reference to an official called
"Lord Preechapiban,"

734
00:59:14,810 --> 00:59:18,190
alleging his involvement

735
00:59:18,300 --> 00:59:20,440
in the illicit opium trade.

736
00:59:20,980 --> 00:59:23,390
However, when the claim

737
00:59:23,420 --> 00:59:25,590
is examined

738
00:59:25,620 --> 00:59:29,940
against other available historical evidence,

739
00:59:30,080 --> 00:59:31,720
it is evident

740
00:59:31,810 --> 00:59:34,680
that this official

741
00:59:34,770 --> 00:59:37,220
was regarded widely

742
00:59:37,600 --> 00:59:41,640
as a person of integrity and probity.

743
00:59:43,880 --> 00:59:45,760
The question here is that...

744
00:59:46,390 --> 00:59:49,530
How was this document...

745
01:00:07,040 --> 01:00:09,840
We discovered this document

746
01:00:09,920 --> 01:00:14,150
buried in an area that was believed to be

747
01:00:14,210 --> 01:00:16,880
the estate of a certain high lord.

748
01:00:17,880 --> 01:00:20,100
In the surrounding area,

749
01:00:20,420 --> 01:00:21,860
there are also Wat Sema Muang

750
01:00:21,900 --> 01:00:25,060
and the canal market
mentioned in the document.

751
01:00:25,090 --> 01:00:27,840
It is probably equivalent to

752
01:00:28,750 --> 01:00:30,160
the ancient Chinese market

753
01:00:30,640 --> 01:00:33,720
by Khlong Takhian,

754
01:00:34,140 --> 01:00:36,080
as it was a vast market

755
01:00:36,310 --> 01:00:38,920
accessible by both boat and land,

756
01:00:39,390 --> 01:00:41,550
consisting of brothels

757
01:00:41,580 --> 01:00:44,720
and countless Chinese establishments.

758
01:00:48,740 --> 01:00:50,520
- Thank you very much.
- Thank you.

759
01:00:56,850 --> 01:00:58,320
It's very close to my mom's place.

760
01:01:00,270 --> 01:01:02,080
What you did in the past

761
01:01:03,020 --> 01:01:04,960
really changed the present.

762
01:01:10,160 --> 01:01:12,840
Do you think
you'll meet Lord Preechapiban?

763
01:01:16,560 --> 01:01:17,680
Maybe not.

764
01:01:20,750 --> 01:01:21,600
Or...

765
01:01:23,170 --> 01:01:24,400
Maybe I already met him.

766
01:01:26,810 --> 01:01:27,560
Phop.

767
01:01:28,440 --> 01:01:30,320
Can you take me to my mom's place?

768
01:02:01,410 --> 01:02:02,440
This day,

769
01:02:03,280 --> 01:02:05,320
I owe you my deepest gratitude.

770
01:02:09,210 --> 01:02:11,320
It brings me joy to see you in such delight.

771
01:02:11,840 --> 01:02:12,840
Rest now.

772
01:02:13,230 --> 01:02:14,960
I shall come fetch you tomorrow.

773
01:02:20,280 --> 01:02:22,130
Would you like a drink

774
01:02:22,150 --> 01:02:23,920
or some snacks first?

775
01:02:25,940 --> 01:02:27,150
Is your mother home?

776
01:02:27,940 --> 01:02:29,120
I don't want to bother her.

777
01:02:29,560 --> 01:02:32,000
Nakun, you're home?

778
01:02:40,740 --> 01:02:41,800
Hello, Mother.

779
01:02:52,680 --> 01:02:53,720
Hello.

780
01:02:53,820 --> 01:02:55,280
Come inside, will you?

781
01:02:55,320 --> 01:02:58,430
I just finished preparing mangoes
and sweet fish sauce dip.

782
01:03:10,620 --> 01:03:12,880
Well, this is a bit strange, isn't it?

783
01:03:12,950 --> 01:03:17,800
You're not usually
into history or archaeology.

784
01:03:17,880 --> 01:03:21,540
You were born in Ayutthaya,
yet you've barely visited any of the sites.

785
01:03:23,510 --> 01:03:25,520
You seem especially happy today, don't you?

786
01:03:27,230 --> 01:03:29,080
Your senior's here
to take you on a trip, huh?

787
01:03:34,950 --> 01:03:35,760
Phop.

788
01:03:36,580 --> 01:03:39,800
I must thank you, and...

789
01:03:40,580 --> 01:03:42,920
please take care of Nakun for me.

790
01:03:47,470 --> 01:03:49,060
Of course, Mother.

791
01:03:55,290 --> 01:03:57,040
Um, the bathroom...

792
01:03:57,080 --> 01:03:57,780
Oh.

793
01:03:58,330 --> 01:04:00,440
It's to the left of the entrance.

794
01:04:00,880 --> 01:04:01,800
Thank you.

795
01:04:13,720 --> 01:04:17,120
Now, no need to be so tense.

796
01:04:18,080 --> 01:04:20,920
Whether he's your friend, your senior,

797
01:04:21,400 --> 01:04:23,360
or your boyfriend,

798
01:04:23,600 --> 01:04:24,960
I've got no problem with it.

799
01:04:25,400 --> 01:04:29,280
I'm really happy for you.

800
01:04:31,540 --> 01:04:32,440
It's not that, Mom.

801
01:04:33,460 --> 01:04:34,640
There's something else on my mind.

802
01:04:42,080 --> 01:04:44,010
Phop

803
01:04:45,340 --> 01:04:47,800
took me on a trip today,

804
01:04:50,260 --> 01:04:51,260
and

805
01:04:53,160 --> 01:04:55,800
I heard a story

806
01:04:56,320 --> 01:04:58,240
about a certain Ayutthaya-era high lord.

807
01:05:01,140 --> 01:05:02,140
Mom, do you know

808
01:05:03,310 --> 01:05:04,980
who Lord Preechapiban was?

809
01:05:15,060 --> 01:05:16,200
I don't.

810
01:05:19,670 --> 01:05:20,640
But...

811
01:05:20,880 --> 01:05:24,160
my old surname used to include 'Preecha.'

812
01:05:24,870 --> 01:05:26,560
'Satjapreecha.'

813
01:05:26,610 --> 01:05:31,080
It means "knowledge rooted in integrity."

814
01:05:32,240 --> 01:05:36,440
Our family really stands by this meaning,

815
01:05:36,470 --> 01:05:38,760
as we are officials.

816
01:05:39,160 --> 01:05:41,000
In our family's eyes,

817
01:05:41,440 --> 01:05:44,860
working as an official
is the same as holding real power.

818
01:05:44,900 --> 01:05:46,020
That means

819
01:05:46,040 --> 01:05:49,760
we must work with dedication and honesty,

820
01:05:49,780 --> 01:05:52,900
and most importantly, never take bribes.

821
01:05:56,310 --> 01:05:57,130
Hey.

822
01:05:57,930 --> 01:05:59,520
Don't tell me

823
01:05:59,760 --> 01:06:00,920
you think

824
01:06:01,010 --> 01:06:03,880
this lord guy
was the forefather of our family.

825
01:06:06,680 --> 01:06:08,480
I think it might be you...

826
01:06:11,390 --> 01:06:12,280
I'm sorry?

827
01:06:22,410 --> 01:06:24,120
You and he are identical.

828
01:06:25,360 --> 01:06:27,250
There's no doubt
that you are his reincarnation.

829
01:06:35,780 --> 01:06:36,940
Forget I said that, Mom.

830
01:06:37,760 --> 01:06:40,300
My mind was all over the place.

831
01:06:45,450 --> 01:06:46,200
Nakun.

832
01:06:50,210 --> 01:06:51,400
Are you sick?

833
01:06:54,380 --> 01:06:55,160
I think

834
01:06:55,840 --> 01:06:57,000
you're burning up.

835
01:06:57,040 --> 01:06:58,180
I think you...

836
01:07:03,950 --> 01:07:04,760
Mom.

837
01:07:06,690 --> 01:07:07,690
I'm...

838
01:07:09,660 --> 01:07:11,140
I'm so grateful

839
01:07:13,240 --> 01:07:14,030
to...

840
01:07:15,640 --> 01:07:17,420
have been born as your son in this life.

841
01:07:32,450 --> 01:07:33,920
What about your next one?

842
01:07:42,950 --> 01:07:44,960
I hope I can be your son in every lifetime.

843
01:08:10,630 --> 01:08:11,930
I love you, sweetie.

844
01:08:14,620 --> 01:08:15,820
I love you too, Mom.

845
01:08:46,189 --> 01:08:48,520
Your mother's house is close to my manor.

846
01:08:48,990 --> 01:08:51,600
That's why you were transported
from the mango orchard to there.

847
01:08:52,420 --> 01:08:53,800
That's why everything and everyone

848
01:08:54,029 --> 01:08:55,520
eventually came back to each other.

849
01:08:59,770 --> 01:09:01,359
Those we don't meet here

850
01:09:02,670 --> 01:09:03,970
may be reincarnated

851
01:09:04,229 --> 01:09:05,399
in a different gender

852
01:09:05,950 --> 01:09:07,279
or appearance,

853
01:09:07,640 --> 01:09:08,800
like my mom.

854
01:09:09,779 --> 01:09:11,279
Though appearances may change,

855
01:09:12,130 --> 01:09:14,960
the mind journeys on.

856
01:09:19,260 --> 01:09:22,040
My professor taught me this
back in the time-travel literature class:

857
01:09:22,560 --> 01:09:24,540
sometimes, when it comes to time travel,

858
01:09:25,080 --> 01:09:27,319
we cannot simply rely on logic,

859
01:09:27,689 --> 01:09:29,240
but instead on emotions,

860
01:09:29,630 --> 01:09:31,760
hope, and fear.

861
01:09:32,720 --> 01:09:34,090
She once asked me,

862
01:09:34,680 --> 01:09:36,260
"You have no fear?"

863
01:09:37,760 --> 01:09:39,560
But now I realize that

864
01:09:43,140 --> 01:09:45,120
after my parents separated,

865
01:09:46,740 --> 01:09:48,920
what I fear is change,

866
01:09:49,840 --> 01:09:51,359
separation,

867
01:09:52,240 --> 01:09:53,600
and love itself,

868
01:09:54,590 --> 01:09:55,930
because I don't want to lose that person.

869
01:10:00,010 --> 01:10:02,800
But after time traveling and meeting you,

870
01:10:04,960 --> 01:10:06,240
what I've come to realize is that

871
01:10:07,330 --> 01:10:09,140
I shouldn't fixate on the past

872
01:10:10,040 --> 01:10:11,220
or be afraid of the future

873
01:10:12,960 --> 01:10:14,200
because right now,

874
01:10:15,100 --> 01:10:16,040
right here,

875
01:10:16,800 --> 01:10:17,840
at this very moment,

876
01:10:21,970 --> 01:10:22,970
the present

877
01:10:24,280 --> 01:10:25,760
is the most valuable to me.

878
01:10:37,640 --> 01:10:38,760
If that's the case,

879
01:10:39,140 --> 01:10:40,760
let's make the most of the present.

880
01:10:44,870 --> 01:10:45,920
Let's take a shower first,

881
01:10:47,360 --> 01:10:48,870
then we can hold each other and sleep.

882
01:10:57,090 --> 01:10:58,020
Well then...

883
01:10:58,750 --> 01:11:00,960
Kindly have the water heated for me.

884
01:11:01,570 --> 01:11:03,280
I dislike bathing in the canal.

885
01:11:04,140 --> 01:11:05,080
It cannot be done,

886
01:11:05,810 --> 01:11:07,130
for there is no canal here.

887
01:11:09,830 --> 01:11:13,100
A whirlpool bathtub
and a water heater await you.

888
01:11:17,330 --> 01:11:18,040
Hey!

889
01:11:22,030 --> 01:11:23,520
Hey, Phop.

890
01:11:40,980 --> 01:11:41,980
It smells so good.

891
01:11:44,040 --> 01:11:45,560
Can we use it every night?

892
01:11:47,090 --> 01:11:49,340
I want to kiss
your head like this every night.

893
01:11:50,720 --> 01:11:51,960
Phop.

894
01:11:53,240 --> 01:11:55,030
Wait until my hair is dry first.

895
01:11:56,650 --> 01:11:58,440
Haven't I waited long enough?

896
01:15:53,080 --> 01:15:54,210
This feels like a dream, doesn't it?

897
01:15:55,260 --> 01:15:57,320
Who would have thought
we'd find our way back to each other again?

898
01:15:58,570 --> 01:16:01,000
It's probably because of
the fortune teller's wishing stone.

899
01:16:03,040 --> 01:16:05,250
Back at the hut by the pond,

900
01:16:06,530 --> 01:16:08,130
when you told me that

901
01:16:08,600 --> 01:16:11,480
Cherd had his men throw
Pim and Kla's bodies into the pond,

902
01:16:12,110 --> 01:16:14,280
I had my patrolmen search for them.

903
01:16:22,680 --> 01:16:24,760
Then, one of my men found something.

904
01:16:52,990 --> 01:16:56,200
The next day,
I went to ask Jom and Kaew about it.

905
01:16:59,870 --> 01:17:01,360
I found out that

906
01:17:01,870 --> 01:17:04,560
the oracle also gave Kaew another stone.

907
01:17:21,930 --> 01:17:23,560
I never understood this:

908
01:17:24,350 --> 01:17:26,930
Klao disappeared when Cherd shot me,

909
01:17:27,520 --> 01:17:30,140
but why was his body
at the bottom of the pond?

910
01:17:45,070 --> 01:17:47,040
Despite that, I kept the stone

911
01:17:47,760 --> 01:17:49,530
until the day I drew my final breath.

912
01:17:56,060 --> 01:17:57,480
I made a wish

913
01:17:57,710 --> 01:17:59,940
to be reincarnated somewhere close to you,

914
01:18:01,230 --> 01:18:03,000
to remember who you were,

915
01:18:03,840 --> 01:18:05,760
and to have a chance to love you once more.

916
01:18:06,960 --> 01:18:09,160
Then I will love you as much as I can.

917
01:18:14,400 --> 01:18:16,520
After that, the light in me simply faded

918
01:18:17,260 --> 01:18:18,520
as I lay there alone.

919
01:18:27,400 --> 01:18:29,800
Maybe it isn't the stone at all,

920
01:18:31,050 --> 01:18:33,040
but rather how much I love

921
01:18:33,730 --> 01:18:35,080
and long for you.

922
01:18:36,410 --> 01:18:37,860
That's why we found each other again.

923
01:18:46,840 --> 01:18:48,200
Well, I'm right here.

924
01:18:50,050 --> 01:18:51,660
I won't keep you waiting anymore.

925
01:18:52,830 --> 01:18:54,440
I won't slip out of your arms, either.

926
01:19:00,020 --> 01:19:01,880
If you do,
I will find my way to you again.

927
01:19:04,250 --> 01:19:06,120
Even if death tears us apart,

928
01:19:07,230 --> 01:19:09,720
I will find my way back to you
in every lifetime.

929
01:19:14,090 --> 01:19:14,920
And...

930
01:19:15,940 --> 01:19:17,880
what if we don't recognize each other
in the next life?

931
01:19:19,050 --> 01:19:19,880
Or...

932
01:19:20,450 --> 01:19:22,480
what if the miracle
doesn't happen next time?

933
01:19:26,740 --> 01:19:27,960
It's not a problem at all.

934
01:19:28,660 --> 01:19:30,920
Let's love each other
as best as we can in this life.

935
01:19:43,740 --> 01:19:46,350
I've imagined this moment in many ways.

936
01:19:48,430 --> 01:19:49,800
How should I ask you?

937
01:19:50,640 --> 01:19:52,000
When would be the right time?

938
01:19:53,190 --> 01:19:54,450
Where would be the perfect place?

939
01:19:56,650 --> 01:19:58,160
But in the end,

940
01:19:59,070 --> 01:20:00,640
I just know this is the moment.

941
01:20:04,520 --> 01:20:05,720
I don't want to wait any longer.

942
01:20:22,850 --> 01:20:25,380
My mom told me this is our family heirloom.

943
01:20:31,500 --> 01:20:33,520
You'll probably graduate in 2025,

944
01:20:35,970 --> 01:20:38,380
just as the Marriage Equality Act
is likely to pass.

945
01:20:44,370 --> 01:20:45,960
When that time comes,

946
01:20:48,350 --> 01:20:49,800
will you be...

947
01:20:50,660 --> 01:20:51,560
wed to me?

948
01:20:57,160 --> 01:20:58,040
Yes.

949
01:20:59,520 --> 01:21:00,360
Certainly,

950
01:21:01,510 --> 01:21:02,320
my Lord.

951
01:21:19,640 --> 01:21:21,080
We met here,

952
01:21:21,350 --> 01:21:22,920
so we want to register our marriage

953
01:21:23,480 --> 01:21:25,040
and get married right here.

954
01:21:26,070 --> 01:21:26,820
Yes.

955
01:21:26,980 --> 01:21:30,000
I want to register our marriage on the day
the Marriage Equality Act passes,

956
01:21:30,680 --> 01:21:32,840
but the date the oracle gave us... Sorry.

957
01:21:33,320 --> 01:21:34,430
I mean, the fortune teller...

958
01:21:34,770 --> 01:21:36,050
It was a different date,

959
01:21:36,250 --> 01:21:37,720
so we chose to register today.

960
01:21:38,080 --> 01:21:40,500
We will then show a special video
for everyone in attendance.

961
01:21:51,770 --> 01:21:53,160
Since meeting Nakun,

962
01:21:53,600 --> 01:21:55,840
Phop has become more talkative and lively.

963
01:21:56,510 --> 01:21:59,560
He hasn't been as sad
and lonely as he used to be.

964
01:22:00,230 --> 01:22:03,320
I guess that's what he gets
from being with Nakun.

965
01:22:03,420 --> 01:22:06,520
When we become one family,

966
01:22:06,760 --> 01:22:08,410
I'm afraid they might end up
talking over each other

967
01:22:08,450 --> 01:22:11,350
and not listening to one another.

968
01:22:11,480 --> 01:22:12,310
I agree.

969
01:22:15,200 --> 01:22:17,200
Cut. Thank you so much.

970
01:22:23,380 --> 01:22:24,440
Hello.

971
01:22:34,290 --> 01:22:38,360
Congratulations.
The Marriage Equality Act is finally official.

972
01:22:39,720 --> 01:22:41,440
I wish you both a beautiful love story.

973
01:22:43,110 --> 01:22:46,200
May I ask who will be signing
as the witness?

974
01:22:51,610 --> 01:22:53,240
Please sign here.

975
01:22:57,230 --> 01:22:58,710
Congratulations, Nakun.

976
01:23:19,730 --> 01:23:21,250
Why are you crying, Thee?

977
01:23:22,410 --> 01:23:23,410
I'm feeling emotional.

978
01:23:23,860 --> 01:23:25,510
Nakun is finally off the market.

979
01:23:27,540 --> 01:23:28,950
Please sign here,

980
01:23:28,980 --> 01:23:30,580
both spouses.

981
01:23:30,640 --> 01:23:31,280
Please give me a moment.

982
01:24:02,750 --> 01:24:04,640
Let me take care of you
until the end of time,

983
01:24:07,530 --> 01:24:08,930
my spouse.

984
01:24:23,880 --> 01:24:26,220
I will also take the best care of you,

985
01:24:27,030 --> 01:24:28,720
to make the wait worth it.

986
01:24:33,510 --> 01:24:35,380
You've both been waiting
a long time for this day, haven't you?

987
01:24:36,090 --> 01:24:36,880
Yes.

988
01:24:37,870 --> 01:24:39,520
For 400 years.

989
01:24:47,920 --> 01:24:50,000
Please sign right here.

990
01:25:10,360 --> 01:25:15,040
I now pronounce you legally married spouses.

991
01:25:16,360 --> 01:25:24,610
♫I solemnly thank Heaven for the love I found♫

992
01:25:24,690 --> 01:25:26,220
And have you not considered it?

993
01:25:26,370 --> 01:25:27,730
How would you and Phop

994
01:25:27,800 --> 01:25:29,080
live together

995
01:25:29,200 --> 01:25:31,160
without inviting cruel gossip?

996
01:25:31,540 --> 01:25:33,280
No good

997
01:25:33,490 --> 01:25:35,270
can come from two men being together,

998
01:25:35,610 --> 01:25:36,960
at least

999
01:25:37,490 --> 01:25:38,720
for the time being.

1000
01:25:39,870 --> 01:25:41,510
If there is a next life,

1001
01:25:42,000 --> 01:25:43,840
I hope we'll meet again

1002
01:25:44,590 --> 01:25:46,440
in a world where men
can fall in love freely.

1003
01:25:46,470 --> 01:25:49,030
♫Forevermore♫

1004
01:25:49,060 --> 01:25:52,060
[Marriage Certificate]

1005
01:25:54,120 --> 01:25:57,130
♫To meet you once again♫

1006
01:25:57,160 --> 01:26:01,760
♫I was born to be your swain♫

1007
01:26:03,240 --> 01:26:07,440
♫Forevermore♫

1008
01:26:07,520 --> 01:26:12,360
[To a love unbound by gender,
standing resolute against the tides of time]

1009
01:26:14,880 --> 01:26:18,880
[Love Upon a Time Series]

1010
01:26:48,880 --> 01:26:56,720
♫I solemnly thank Heaven for the love I found♫

1011
01:26:56,790 --> 01:27:02,270
♫For you, I would gather stars all around♫

1012
01:27:02,310 --> 01:27:12,490
♫The endless ocean
I once waded through was no coincidence♫

1013
01:27:13,350 --> 01:27:16,370
♫To meet you once again♫

1014
01:27:16,420 --> 01:27:21,690
♫My heart and soul are yours, forevermore♫

1015
01:27:22,070 --> 01:27:31,080
♫Though countless tales may come to pass,
so long as you hold my hand♫

1016
01:27:31,130 --> 01:27:42,290
♫I vow to love and cherish you,
our love shall ever stand♫

1017
01:27:42,310 --> 01:27:47,240
♫Solely you and I, we're heartbound♫

1018
01:27:47,270 --> 01:27:48,270
[Love Upon a Time Series]
